{"type": "article", "id": 30278, "title": "智能泳记", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-28T23:01:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160728173708OP2DzovAyiW5aFxG.png", "contents": "<p>          </p><p><a href=\"http://www.platysens.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Platysens</a> 是一家成立于香港的初创公司，自 2014 年起就开始研发与运动项目有关的产品，最近它推出了一款名为 Marlin 的智能泳记，可以通过骨传导的方式让游泳者知道自己的运动信息。有了这样一款头戴式设备，人们在游泳时不再需要为了查看数据而停下来查看运动手表。Marlin 内置的传感器会记录下速度、距离等基本信息，通过语音即时告知用户，而且这些信息也会同步在配套的应用上，免去了额外用纸笔在泳池边记录的麻烦。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2064490284/marlin-the-worlds-first-swim-meter-designed-to-tal\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，附带 GPS 功能的版本为 80 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">&nbsp;<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607281750019OFvRWs4JdpNaMIS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.879828\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728175001NMKcPzwi0BA86kCh.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.814706\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728175002Tz1NlFxjSKRqBpAI.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.063235\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}